Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:22.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be5\c&H000000&\t(0,1000,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H265DAE&)}nakonec skončí se srdcem zlomeným?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:27.95,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\3c&H018662&}Ochraň je!
